graph TD
    Client[Incoming Request] -->|HTTP| Gateway(FastAPI Middleware)
    
    subgraph "living-limiter (Python Asyncio + C++ Core)"
        Gateway -->|Extract Headers| Interceptor(Sentinel Interceptor)
        Interceptor --> Factory{Strategy Factory}
        
        Factory -->|"@rate_limit(strategy=TOKEN_BUCKET)"| TB[Token Bucket Engine]
        Factory -->|"@rate_limit(strategy=LEAKY_BUCKET)"| LB[Leaky Bucket Engine]
        Factory -->|"@rate_limit(strategy=FIXED_WINDOW)"| FW[Fixed Window Engine]
        Factory -->|"@rate_limit(strategy=SLIDING_WINDOW)"| SW[Sliding Window Engine]
    end

    subgraph "Distributed Persistence"
        TB -->|"C++ Redis Sync"| Redis[(Global Redis Vault)]
        LB -->|"C++ Redis Sync"| Redis
        FW -->|"C++ Redis Sync"| Redis
        SW -->|"C++ Redis Sync"| Redis
    end

    Redis -.->|"Decision (Allow/Deny)"| Interceptor
    
    Interceptor -.->|"429 Too Many Requests"| Client
    Interceptor -->|Proceed| Controller(Upstream FastAPI Route)
